Exercise: Create a Visual Report Showing a Count of Skyscrapers by Country and City

Objective:
- Display the number of skyscrapers per country using a bar chart.
- Enable drill-down to show skyscraper counts per city within each country.

Steps Taken:
- Used the provided Power BI report file.
- Created a bar chart with conditional formatting based on skyscraper count.
- Added a hierarchy with Country and City fields.
- Enabled Drill Mode to allow navigation from country-level to city-level data.
- Styled the chart title and applied data labels inside bars.
